{{no footnotes|date=February 2013}} The '''Max Planck Institute for Dynamics of Complex Technical Systems''' is located in [[Magdeburg]], [[Germany]]. It was founded in 1996. It is one of 80 institutes in the [[Max Planck Society]] (Max Planck Gesellschaft).
